description:
The "Basic" Aromatherapy Blending Kit contains:

5 Essential Oils:  Bergamot (1/3 oz / 10 ml), Geranium (1/3 oz / 10 ml), Lavender (1/3 oz / 10 ml), Tangerine (1/3 oz / 10 ml), and Ylang Ylang (1/8 oz / 3.75 ml);

1 Bottle of 100% pure HobaCare Jojoba Carrier Oil (1 oz / 29.6 ml);

2 Empty 1/3 oz. glass roll-on bottles;

12 Unscented sniffers;

Blending box;

Plastic carrying case; and

Handouts and charts.

(Guide book is sold separately.)

(Reg. Price:  $95)

"Complete" Aromatherapy Blending Kit contains:

9 Essential Oils:  Bergamot (1/3 oz / 10 ml), Eucalyptus (1/2 oz / 15 ml),  Geranium (1/3 oz / 10 ml), Lavender (1/3 oz / 10 ml), Peppermint (1/3 oz / 10 ml), Rosemary (1/2 oz / 15 ml), Tangerine (1/3 oz / 10 ml), Tea Tree (1/3 oz / 10 ml), and Ylang Ylang (1/8 oz / 3.75 ml);

2 Bottles of 100% pure HobaCare Jojoba Carrier Oil (1 oz / 29.6 ml);

2 Empty 1/3 oz. glass roll-on bottles;

12 Unscented sniffers;

Blending box;

Plastic carrying case; and

Handouts and charts.

(Guide book is sold separately.)

(Reg. Price: $130)

"Mini" Aromatherapy Blending Kit contains (For workshop use--will include use of aromatherapy oils during class):

1 Bottle of 100% pure HobaCare Jojoba Carrier Oil (1 oz / 29.6 ml);

1 Glass roll-on bottle filled with 100% pure HobaCare Jojoba Carrier Oil (1/3 oz / 10 ml); and

3 Unscented Sniffers;

Blending box;

Plastic carrying case; and

Handouts and charts.

(Guide book is sold separately.)

(Reg. Price:  $15)
